{% set useBluePageHeader = true %}
{% extends 'layout.njk' %}

{% from 'components/action-link/macro.njk' import actionLink %}

{% block content %}
  <div class="nhsuk-grid-row">
    <div class="nhsuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
      <h1 class="nhsuk-heading-l">
          UI Toolkit
          <span class="nhsuk-caption-l nhsuk-caption--bottom">Prototype and build things better</span>
      </h1>

      <p>The main scope of this project is to streamline traditional UI stack (<b>HTML + CSS + JS</b>) workflows and incorporate best practices for both UI development and UX research when building <a href="https://service-manual.nhs.uk/design-system">NHSUK</a> or <a href="https://design-system.service.gov.uk/">GOVUK</a> digital services.</p>
      <p>The project uses  <a href="https://gulpjs.com/">Gulp 4</a>, <a href="https://webpack.js.org/">Webpack 4</a>, <a href="https://github.com/sass/node-sass">Node SASS</a>, <a href="https://babeljs.io/docs/en/">Babel</a> to build production-ready front-end assets using the NHSUK or GOVUK front-end toolkit (or no toolkit at all if you just fancy vanilla üç¶).</p>
      <p>The project is also a static site gerenator - creating HTML pages from <a href="https://mozilla.github.io/nunjucks/templating.html">Nunjucks</a> templates, so it can be used for prototyping.</p>

      {{ actionLink({
        "text": "Find out more about this project",
        "href": "https://github.com/valtech-uk/ui-toolkit"
      }) }}
  </div>
{% endblock %}
